commit.title: [ci] [gh-actions] Initial setup of Windows Github Build
commit.message:
[ci] [gh-actions] Initial setup of Windows Github Build

This was started from the very nice work of Jason Gross at

https://github.com/mit-plv/fiat-crypto/blob/master/.github/workflows/coq-windows.yml

This is obviously a work-in-progress and quite a few things remain to
be done. In particular:

- We should split the script in 4 phases:
  - CYGWIN setup
  - Install of deps
  - Coq build
  - Coq addons build
- We need to deploy the installer
